dct_title_s: Carte détaillée des environs de Paris
dct_description_sm: Bar scale in "Lieues communes de France de 25 au Degré"
Shows various sizes of towns, roads, paths, borders, forests, post offices ("une Poste, une Poste 1/4...1/2...3/4")
Covers area from le Havre to just past Troyes
